The film revolves around the protagonist Robert who sets off on a journey to a remote village called Odeyana Samudra to find answers to the dreams that bother him every single day. In this process he discovers more than what he wanted to know! Is Robert who he really thought he was until today ? Is there past life connection between wildlife photographer Robert and King Randhawa? Does the notorious Spot bellied eagle owl/devil owl bring the connection between the two time zones ? Is the world we live in an illusion by itself ? Is there time travel ? Does Robert find the answers to his questions ? Get ready for this exciting & thrilling rollercoaster journey from the year 1827 to 2019 & back !! Seatbelts on !
